Package dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.output

Class ModuleMetadata

java.lang.Object
dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.output.ModuleMetadata
Direct Known Subclasses:
AiccMetadata, Cmi5Metadata, Scorm12Metadata, Scorm2004Metadata
public abstract class ModuleMetadata extends Object
Represents the core metadata for an eLearning module, providing common fields shared across various module types, such as SCORM, AICC, or xAPI.

Each module type can extend this class to include additional fields specific to that type.
